e heard some conflicting reports so I wanted to ask those who know. Should I use taunt everytime it pops up or would it have no effect  when the mob is on me and should I only press it once it turns to someone else?<br>
<br>
Also I am planning to make a macro for taunt. I will put taunt and disarm in there for sure. What I was wondering whether or not it is worth it to /sit on /sit off /attack on mid combat? The transition is very fast but do I lose more aggro from combat than I gain by sitting?<br>
<br>
<br>
